{
  "application": "gromacs",
  "software": [
    "gcc91",
    "openmpi-3.0.0",
    "BLAS",
    "gsl-2.5",
    "lapack-3.7.0",
    "cuda-11.3",
    "plumed"
  ],
  "resources": {
    "nodes": 1,
    "cpus": 32,
    "mpiprocs": 16,

    "walltime": "00:05:00",

  "environment_variables": {
    "OMP_NUM_THREADS": 2,
    "LD_LIBRARY_PATH": "/home/giuseppe.gambini/usr/installations/plumed/lib"
  },
  "commands": [
    "module load gcc91",
    "module load openmpi-3.0.0",
    "module load BLAS",
    "module load gsl-2.5",
    "module load lapack-3.7.0",
    "module load cuda-11.3",
    "cd $PBS_O_WORKDIR",
    "export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/home/giuseppe.gambini/usr/installations/plumed/lib",
    "source /home/giuseppe.gambini/usr/src/gmx_plumed.sh",
    "export OMP_NUM_THREADS=2",
    "/apps/openmpi-3.0.0/bin/mpirun -np 16 /home/giuseppe.gambini/usr/installations/gromacs/bin/gmx_mpi mdrun -s ../../md_meta.tpr -plumed meta.dat"
  ]
}
